selectSql:
select
	s.id id,
	case when s.obrigatorio = 'S' then true else false end as obrigatorio,
	s.idservico id_servico,
	s.idservicovinculado id_servico_vinculado
from servicovinculado s
insertSql:
insert into ${SCHEMA}.servico_vinculado (
	id,
	obrigatorio,
	id_servico,
	id_servico_vinculado)
